description: Dieser Datensatz enthält monatliche Werte seit 1983 bis zum Oktober 2023. title_en: Daily updated air quality measurements, since 1983
description_en: This dataset is includes monthly values since 1983 up to October 2023. It is derived from the upstream dataset provided by Stadt Zürich, which contains daily data divided into annual files. In this aggregated dataset, we include daily means for sulphur dioxide (SO2), carbon monoxide (CO), nitrogen oxide (NOx), nitrogen monoxide (NO), nitrogen dioxide (NO2), particulate matter (PM10 and PM2.5) and particle number (PN), if available in sufficient quality. All values are averaged per month. From the 4 location in the upstream dataset, only measurements from Zch_Stampfenbachstrasse were taken into account, as it was available over the whole time range.

title_en: Permanent resident population by gender and nationality
description_en: The data set contains the permanent resident population in persons by communes, gender and nationality (two categories: Switzerland and abroad) as of 2003. The permanent resident population includes all persons with their main place of residence in the canton of Schwyz. The foreign population includes persons with a settlement permit (C), residence permit (B) or short-term residence permit (L) of 12 months or more. The population is listed in persons as at 31.12.
